{"id":"5215a6c6f1f217e9cdfaf69c36256d8334b7204a24fdb7a4f153929f9957fe48","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:0","text":"Sample filter 和 display filter 插件分别用于在"}
{"id":"168196d133817ed25c3fe0bf9a5254309ab899daa622e81d3ead0daf0eb33def","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:1","text":"integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"058b4840ac5f3322a12280d0229f232a824ab41b2e7666524e395635f5c464ed","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:2","text":"生成着色采样和像素值之后，并在它们发送到"}
{"id":"78198ae6c8b8a723b50b172b1d245b55576bbabd66e732297e75f2e47a693f1c","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:3","text":"display driver（显示驱动器）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:4","text":"之前，对这些值进行调整。"}
{"id":"f7d5cf2be92e577d7924a8529697395f00026b759d2b0fe5b5f3a2c3ef7d6817","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:5","text":"Sample Filters（采样滤镜）"}
{"id":"cc771598ef41782ca75003916c5129b4d7f3645bc9f3ff131367be98ea2d23cb","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:6","text":"Sample Filter（采样滤镜）"}
{"id":"422b1fc7a10439042a65caabf55d57bf10c850e60880852157c659712165614f","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:7","text":"插件描述的是在像素过滤之前对采样值进行的颜色变换。它们作用于尚未应用像素过滤的原始 camera ray samples（相机光线采样）。一旦采样滤镜修改了某个采样并将其写入 framebuffer（帧缓冲），该修改就会永久成为所有渲染图像（包括深度图像）的一部分。请注意，如果单个"}
{"id":"417aba3c51bd81e67c07b7e9a9e61f7cc225dfe190295981b1dba5250c6aa770","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:8","text":"任意输出变量（AOV）"}
{"id":"ff653e0f87c99774e90767244fc483bcab3f908608ac9460568d8d629fadd465","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:9","text":"作为多个图像文件的一部分输出，则对某个采样的一次修改可能会影响所有这些图像。采样滤镜所做的修改也会影响 adaptive sampler（自适应采样器）。"}
{"id":"95f93a137f4633b77974a79cbf12de354b72349ed288ca7c5b0dfce2717ff1b1","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:10","text":"PxrSampleFilterCombiner"}
{"id":"34021bf7c8c11bc51d9f4a4805b32dfa1ca922929d25a857da00d4e07f43e885","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:11","text":"PxrCryptomatte"}
{"id":"d0a3685b5745c118995bdbd69c8417c6d8124e1c6a7b38674e49e2c778212e97","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:12","text":"Display Filters（显示滤镜）"}
{"id":"ca675faca5ce049d2ff740d82ef01014d9327aa568ef4fe4051fed9fc6fe8044","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:13","text":"Display Filter（显示滤镜）"}
{"id":"fe497f84bd3949b1429cbd4c8d3571f1493b034c35c4bbf12cb85afc7fa57a39","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:14","text":"插件描述的是在像素过滤之后、输出之前对最终像素值进行的颜色变换。多个图像共享的 AOV 在此时会被视为彼此独立，因此可以分别修改。目前 Display filters 不支持 deep images（深度图像），并且不会影响 adaptive sampler（自适应采样器）。"}
{"id":"a2c5ac17be505e31cc8432c56a6615299acfcafd5d305d4a1dde83ab696e02e6","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:15","text":"PxrLightSaturation"}
{"id":"acf30b4d4596d552b3b91abd504f07cbd77e421f3e4529d2f5b56ac7065d771f","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:16","text":"PxrDisplayFilterCombiner"}
{"id":"67add60998b58cd8177311d29207705d8aeb83b3d0f93d340d7c4f729bc66d3c","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:17","text":"PxrImageDisplayFilter"}
{"id":"5f0bf599d9e733062f55d2d1c4bdcc5ac3240a508f846a4d5f7cbdeb501fb83d","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:18","text":"PxrShadowDisplayFilter"}
{"id":"3cc72d6d768a5359a267034294144ba8de53c6a6800a374d0af86512d77e4501","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:19","text":"Blender 设置"}
{"id":"87a879104801ea8c795b305bc6f6dca5a25644da34bb0a9544ce605d3e2674cc","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:20","text":"可以创建"}
{"id":"797e06a825245bc5e0fbd82a182c1510b17b6f01d5cd6316407320bc4bef9bfc","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:21","text":"Display and Sample Filters（Display Filters 和 Sample Filters）"}
{"id":"d6520c05526911100723f6603181640726ecb4537a516761b55d87a07e5a29a6","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:22","text":"，位置在渲染属性中"}
{"id":"2a583a8b87f20791563599dfea07b726e834d0ce422464623a4a1f60e2a96cec","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:23","text":"。点击 Add RenderMan Display Filters Nodetree 按钮，或点击 Add RenderMan Sample Filters Nodetree。"}
{"id":"e93c17826d39a166e0b3e8ba9dd2b9df0e89e7802ef57326f33d7aac0ed3d0d3","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:24","text":"你应该会看到 Display Filters 和 Sample Filters 面板展开，类似下图。"}
{"id":"0b2575d64332f5d2bd731079477c5728232ffc24dae2db750a018c558c3c9b05","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:25","text":"点击 Add RenderMan Display Filters Nodetree 会自动添加 PxrBackgroundDisplayFilter 节点，并继承 World color（世界颜色）作为背景色。"}
{"id":"8257a9f9d08cc8270f9ce60556b757088113f1e1e23588ece4bc45f06ae5d18e","item_id":"e3a0d3b5ec:26","text":"可以使用多个 Display and Sample Filters。点击 Add 会新增一个槽位，用于添加额外的 Display Filter 或 Sample Filter。若要移除某个滤镜，请点击名称旁边的 - 按钮。与 integrators（积分器）类似，显示滤镜和采样滤镜本质上都是 World 节点内部的着色节点。"}
